value.0: You are Bloodsworn to a Seelie Fey. This means you support and aid the Court of Dreams. You defend and protect all that holds beauty and support a persons dreams, making sure they do not give up on them. While you respect both sides of the balance, you yourself work for the light, the summer, the beautiful dream.
